The trace norm of `c • A` is `RCLike.re (CFC.sqrt ((c • A).conjTranspose * (c • A))).trace`. By our hypothesis, we can rewrite the argument to `CFC.sqrt` as `↑‖c‖ ^ 2 • (A.conjTranspose * A)`. 

