# Solving the `sorry` in the `traceNorm_smul` Proof

The error occurs in the proof of `traceNorm_smul`, specifically when trying to establish the equality:
`CFC.sqrt (↑‖c‖ ^ 2 • (A.conjTranspose * A)) = ↑‖c‖ • CFC.sqrt (A.conjTranspose * A)`.

The relevant part of the code is:
```tactics
  rw [traceNorm, h]
  open MatrixOrder in
  have : RCLike.re (trace (‖c‖ • CFC.sqrt (A.conjTranspose * A))) = ‖c‖ * traceNorm A := by
    simp [RCLike.smul_re]
    apply Or.inl
    rfl
